# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok an iraqi delegation led by defense minister abdel qader mohammed jassim arrived in ankara on thursday seeking to avert a turkish military incursion against kurd rebels in northern iraq .
# ::alignments
(a / arrive-01
      :ARG1 (d / delegation
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Iraq"))
            :ARG1-of (l / lead-02
                  :ARG0 (p / person
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Abdel"
                              :op2 "Qader"
                              :op3 "Mohammed"
                              :op4 "Jassim")
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG2 (m / minister
                                    :topic (d2 / defend-01)))))
            :ARG0-of (s / seek-01
                  :ARG1 (a2 / avert-01
                        :ARG0 d
                        :ARG1 (ii / incursion
                              :mod (m2 / military)
                              :prep-against (p2 / person
                                    :ARG0-of (r / rebel-01)
                                    :mod (e / ethnic-group
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Kurd"))
                                    :location (n4 / north
                                          :part-of c))
                              :mod (r2 / religious-group
                                    :name (n5 / name
                                          :op1 "Turkish"))))))
      :ARG4 (c2 / city
            :name (n6 / name
                  :op1 "Ankara"))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok europe 's food safety agency recommended wednesday that manufacturers of bottled baby food change the packaging as soon as possible because of cancer concerns over a chemical found in some foods packed in glass jars with metal lids .
# ::alignments
(r / recommend-01
      :ARG0 (a / agency
            :mod (s / safe-01
                  :ARG1 (f / food))
            :poss (c / continent
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Europe")))
      :ARG1 (c2 / change-01
            :ARG0 (c3 / company
                  :ARG0-of (m / manufacture-01
                        :ARG1 (f2 / food
                              :mod (b / baby)
                              :ARG1-of (b2 / bottle-01))))
            :ARG1 (t / thing
                  :ARG2-of (p / package-01))
            :time (s2 / soon
                  :ARG2-of (h / have-degree-91
                        :ARG1 c2
                        :ARG3 (e / equal)
                        :ARG4 (p2 / possible-01
                              :ARG1 c2))))
      :ARG1-of (c4 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (c5 / concern-01
                  :ARG0 (c6 / chemical
                        :ARG1-of (f3 / find-01
                              :location (f4 / food
                                    :ARG1-of (p3 / pack-01
                                          :ARG2 (j / jar
                                                :consist-of (m2 / metal)
                                                :part-of (g / glass))
                                          :mod (s3 / some)))))
                  :ARG1 (c7 / cancer)))
      :time (w / wednesday))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok north korea said thursday it would reactivate a mothballed nuclear program because of a us decision to cut off fuel aid , raising the stakes in a rapidly escalating confrontation .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (c / country
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "North"
                  :op2 "Korea"))
      :ARG1 (r / reactivate-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (p / program
                  :mod (n2 / nucleus)
                  :ARG1-of (m / mothball-01))
            :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (d / decide-01
                        :ARG0 (c3 / country
                              :name n
                              :op1 "United"
                              :op2 "States"))
                  :ARG1 (c4 / cut-off-04
                        :ARG0 c3
                        :ARG1 (a / aid-01
                              :ARG1 (f / fuel)))))
      :ARG0-of (r2 / raise-01
            :ARG1 (s2 / stakes
                  :topic (c5 / confront-01
                        :ARG1-of (e / escalate-01
                              :manner (r3 / rapid)))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :ARG1-of (f2 / frequent-02)
                  :ARG0-of (p / plague-01
                        :ARG1 (u / utility
                              :ARG1-of (r2 / run-01
                                    :ARG0 (s / state))))
                  :time (s2 / since
                        :op1 (d / date-entity
                              :month 2
                              :time-of (r3 / reserve-01
                                    :ARG0 r
                                    :ARG1 (m / multiple
                                          :op1 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                                                :quant 1000000
                                                :unit (d2 / dollar)))
                                    :purpose (u2 / upgrade-02
                                          :ARG0 r
                                          :ARG1 (s3 / safe-01
                                                :ARG1 (t / travel-01)))))))
            :ARG1-of (l / long-03
                  :ARG2 (t2 / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 1
                        :unit (m3 / month))))
      :time d
      :weekday (m4 / monday))

# ::alignments
(r / reject-01
      :ARG0 (p / party
            :ARG0-of (o / oppose-01)
            :mod (m / main)
            :location (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Zimbabwe")
                  :part (s / south)))
      :ARG1 (r2 / result-01
            :ARG1 (e / elect-01
                  :ARG2 (m2 / mayor)
                  :ARG1-of (w / win-01
                        :ARG0 (p2 / party
                              :ARG0-of (r3 / rule-03))
                        :location (c2 / city
                              :mod (c3 / center)
                              :location s)
                        :time (w2 / week
                              :mod (t / this)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / tuesday))
      :ARG0-of (c4 / cause-01
            :ARG1 (c5 / claim-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (d2 / defraud-01
                        :ARG1 e))))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (o / official
                        :mod (s2 / senior)
                        :ARG1-of (c / charge-05
                              :ARG2 (a / administer-01
                                    :ARG1 (ii / industry
                                          :mod (ii2 / information)))))))
      :ARG1 (e / encourage-01
            :ARG0 (c2 / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "China"))
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (e2 / enterprise
                        :ARG1-of (s3 / size-01
                              :ARG2 (s4 / small)))
                  :op2 (e3 / enterprise
                        :ARG1-of (s5 / size-01
                              :ARG2 (m / medium))))
            :ARG2 (s6 / set-01
                  :ARG0 a2
                  :ARG1 (f / foot)
                  :ARG2 (m2 / market
                        :mod (t / telecommunication)
                        :ARG1-of (a3 / add-02
                              :ARG2 (v / value)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s7 / saturday))
      :location (h2 / here))

      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (p2 / prosecute-01))
      :ARG1 (a / arrest-01

                  :ARG0-of (n / nurse-01)

                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Berlin")))
            :ARG2 (s2 / suspect-01
                  :ARG1 (k / kill-01
                        :ARG0 p3
                        :ARG1 (p4 / person
                              :quant 2
                              :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91
                                    :ARG1 p3
                                    :ARG2 (p5 / patient)))
                        :location (u / unit
                              :mod (c / cardiology)))
                  :ARG2 p3))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

      :ARG1 (s2 / series
            :ARG1-of (e / expect-01)
            :consist-of (a2 / announce-01
                  :ARG0 (n3 / nation
                        :ARG1-of (a3 / ally-01))
                  :ARG1 (s3 / support-01
                        :ARG0 n3
                        :ARG1 (e2 / effort-01
                              :ARG1 (w2 / war)
                              :location (c / country
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Afghanistan")))
                        :mod (a4 / additional)
                        :mod (m / military)
                        :mod (c2 / civilian)
                        :mod (f3 / finance)))))

                  :op1 "Qatar"))

                  :op1 "International"
                  :op2 "Court"
                  :op3 "of"

            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (r2 / refute-01
